## Data Usage Disclaimer

This project uses publicly available data from:
- Scryfall API (https://scryfall.com/docs/api) - Magic: The Gathering card data
- Pokemon TCG API (https://pokemontcg.io/) - Pokemon Trading Card Game data
- Public tournament deck lists from various tournament sites

**Important Notes:**
- This project stores only **metadata** (card names, types, colors, mana costs, etc.)
- **No copyrighted card text** (oracle text, flavor text) is stored in this repository
- **No card artwork or images** are stored in this repository
- Card names are factual data and are generally not subject to copyright protection
- All data is used in accordance with the terms of service of the respective APIs

**Game Content:**
- Magic: The Gathering is a trademark of Wizards of the Coast LLC
- Pokemon is a trademark of Nintendo, Creatures Inc., and Game Freak Inc.
- This project is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by these companies

**Fair Use:**
This project is intended for research and educational purposes. Commercial use may
require appropriate licensing from game publishers.
